title: All Star Summoner Icon
body: I used all 25 of my votes and am looking forward to all the all star games!! Unfortunately i realized that i never got the summoner icon for doing so. I dont know if it takes awhile or not, but a friend of mine got his almost immediately. plz help!!

replies.body:
Hey PMoN3y757,

Some icons do take a bit of time to make their way to your account. Are you still experiencing this?
thats what i figured. I voted two days ago, and no i still dont see it :( i tried restarting client still nothin
Hmm. If you don't receive it soon, I would toss a ticket to [Player Support](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new?ticket_form_id=4584). They'd be able to help you out! ^-^
